detect evil and good
Level-1st
CastingTime-1Action
Range/Area-Self
School-Divination
Attack/Save-div
OtherInfo-                For the duration, you know if there is an aberration, celestial, elemental, fey, fiend, or undead within 30 feet of you, as well as where the creature is located. Similarly, you know if there is a lace or object within 30 feet of you that has been magically consecrated or desecrated.
